	(layer "F.Cu")
	(descr "1206 (3216 metric) IR LED, polarity per Everlight IR15-21C/TR8 datasheet: PAD 1 = ANODE, PAD 2 = CATHODE (cathode mark on pad-2 side). This is the OPPOSITE of the stock KiCad LED_SMD convention (pad1=cathode); made explicit so JLC pin1->pad1 placement and hand assembly both land the anode on pad 1.")
